{
  "stem": "6777.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, it was said at that time that they are being transported to arbeitslager.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That means work camps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And apparently, it was true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Part-- part of the people have been kept in, say, Lublin ghetto, which was, for quite a long time, a working place.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But some, especially the old ones and the young ones, who have been not-- nonproductive, so to say, they have been straight into the ovens and to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was Auschwitz and Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember Korczak.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You may have heard about Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Korczak.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the Pole--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know him?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I've seen him marching on top of the column of his children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was offered to be exempted, but he didn't accept it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went with his children, knowing that it is for death.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Adam Czerniakow?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he got to know that the exterminations are taking place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He wasn't told that it will be final because the final solution didn't-- has not been decreed till much later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he got to know that the people who are being taken out apparently will be gassed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, after the first aktion, there came a couple of people, young blokes, back, because they wrapped themselves into the clothing which have been left by the people who went into the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the clothing has been loaded into trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the train came to Warsaw, somehow or another, a couple of people came out and came back into the ghetto and told the Judenrat what's really happening and where the supposed work camps-- what really happens there.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At that time, a lot of people wouldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Disbelief.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
